      "source": [
        "import math\n",
        "\n",
        "def f(x):\n",
        "  return math.exp(x) - x - 2"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "2. Definisikan turunan fungsi f(x) sebagai f'(x) = e^x - 1:"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "45nTTT5SZycd"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "def f_prime(x):\n",
        "  return math.exp(x) - 1"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "zDaBCeaHZ5Gj"
      },
      "execution_count": 2,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "3. Definisikan metode Newton-Raphson dengan Python:"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "zEDblfYVZ-5v"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "def newton_raphson(x0, tol):\n",
        "  x = x0\n",
        "  fx = f(x)\n",
        "  iteration = 0\n",
        "  while abs(fx) > tol:\n",
        "    x = x - fx / f_prime(x)\n",
        "    fx = f(x)\n",
        "    iteration += 1\n",
        "  return x, iteration"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "hJLUSZpxaDbS"
      },
      "execution_count": 3,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "4. Gunakan metode Newton-Raphson dengan perkiraan awal x0 = -10 dan x0 = 10 dan batas toleransi 0,000001:"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "NtKwd5ROaO5H"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "x1, iteration1 = newton_raphson(-10, 0.000001)\n",
        "x2, iteration2 = newton_raphson(10, 0.000001)"
